  %section.stakeholders.width
    %article
      %h2 Students
      %p Whether you're coming from another career or already know some programming, you probably have a lot of questions about this program. Click here to get started on your way to a career full of creativity and joy.
      .call-to-action
        %a.button{:href => "/program.html"} Learn More
    %article
      %h2 Employers
      %p Finding awesome people that work hard and get along with clients can be hard. We've done the work for you; all you need to do is find the student that matches your company style and show them where to sit.
